===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|dot one's i's and cross one's t's}}
* {{l|en|cross the i's and dot the t's}} {{qualifier|humorous}}

===Etymology===
In reference to {{m|en|cursive}} ({{m|en|joined up}}) writing, where adding the dot to the letter ''i'' and the crossbar to the letter ''t'' is done after one reaches the end of the word and thus may be forgotten if one is not being careful.

